  "name": "Floating Shield",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>A <em>floating shield</em> is usually carved with wing motifs. This buckler (Hardness 6, HP 24, BT 12) can protect you on its own.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The shield magically releases itself and floats off your arm into the air next to you, granting you its bonus automatically, as if you had Raised the Shield.</p>\n<p>Because you're not wielding the shield, you can't use reactions such as Shield Block with the shield, but you gain its benefits even when using both of your hands.</p>\n<p>After 1 minute, the shield drops to the ground, ending its floating effect. While the shield is adjacent to you, you can Interact to grasp it, ending its floating effect early.</p>"
    },
